rows.label: qst702007_msg0001
rows.name: This is Superbia?

rows.label: qst702007_msg0002
rows.name: It's different from what I imagined...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0003
rows.name: This is Aletta, in Iira.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0004
rows.name: Why are we in Iira?

rows.label: qst702007_msg0005
rows.name: Because...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0006
rows.name: Look.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0007
rows.name: Dad!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0008
rows.name: Kai! Kei!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0009
rows.name: I'm so glad. You're really safe!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0010
rows.name: We finally get to see you!

rows.label: qst702007_msg0011
rows.name: I'm so glad...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0012
rows.name: I'm so, so happy... I'm moved...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0013
rows.name: He's crying again...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0014
rows.name: Adel-sama, thank you so much for this.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0015
rows.name:
No... However, I'm sorry
to hear about your wife.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0016
rows.name: Yes...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0017
rows.name: But my children are here...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0018
rows.name: That alone is a great comfort.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0019
rows.name:
I will do my best for
Nelly's sake as well.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes... But don't push
yourself too hard.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0021
rows.name:
You too, Adel-sama. You're the
type to get involved in everything,
so please don't overdo it.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0022
rows.name: Don't worry.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0023
rows.name:
Everyone here is a meddler,
so I think Adel's burden
has been lightened.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0024
rows.name: Hahaha...

rows.label: qst702007_msg0025
rows.name: Thanks, big bro.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0026
rows.name: Thanks to you too, big sis.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0027
rows.name:
We'll be living here from now
on, so nice to meet you.

rows.label: qst702007_msg0028
rows.name: Yes, same here. Welcome, Kai and Kei.
